					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Equivalent of this is going on in 4MByte + SRAM carts.<br /><br /><img src="http://www.tmeeco.eu/BitShit/Doodles/4MBwithSRAM.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br />Write to A130xx range pulses !TIME pin, that is used to latch the value of D0 line which controls whether or not upper 2MBytes are ROM or SRAM. 1 = RAM, 0 = ROM.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.tmeeco.eu">http://www.tmeeco.eu</a><!-- m --></div>
